AGENT SPECIALIZATION EXAMPLES:

GOOD SPECIALIZATION:
- "SQLi Fuzzing Agent (Login)" - skills: sql_injection
- "XSS Validation Agent (Search)" - skills: xss
- "Auth Testing Agent" - skills: authentication_jwt, business_logic
- "SSRF + XXE Agent" - skills: ssrf, xxe (related vectors)

